sources.description:
A mysterious ex-cop named Isaiah Slade arrives at the small town funeral of ranch owner Robert Marks. As he informs different members of the community that he knew Robert and is there to help find the youngest daughter who is still missing, Slade is forced to navigate this rural noir world of shady characters, dishonest answers and his own personal demons to try and get to the truth.
2022.  Stars: Nick McCallum, Stelio Savante, Anais Lilit
